    <item>
      <title>Mol 首席执行官称乌克兰对卢克石油的制裁不太可能导致短缺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/ukraine-s-lukoil-sanctions-unlikely-to-cause-shortage-mol-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[炼油商 Mol Nyrt 的首席执行官表示，匈牙利不会因为乌克兰决定阻止卢克石油 PJSC 原油的运输而遭受石油短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/ukraine-s-lukoil-sanctions-unlikely-to-cause-shortage-mol-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:54:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>先锋集团首席执行官致力于为私人资产带来低成本投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/vanguard-ceo-aims-to-bring-low-cost-investing-to-private-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[先锋集团首席执行官萨利姆·拉姆吉 (Salim Ramji) 表示，他的公司“真正致力于”低成本投资，并且他最终希望将这种理念带入私人资产领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/vanguard-ceo-aims-to-bring-low-cost-investing-to-private-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国债价格上涨引发美联储需要多快降息的争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/us-two-year-yield-below-10-year-for-first-time-since-july-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[规模达 27 万亿美元的美国国债市场大幅上涨，暴露出人们对美国经济陷入衰退以及美联储需要开始大幅降息的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/us-two-year-yield-below-10-year-for-first-time-since-july-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可腐败调查以瑞士罚款结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/glencore-ordered-to-pay-150-million-by-swiss-in-criminal-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士当局结束对这家大宗商品交易商和矿业公司的调查后，嘉能可公司将支付 1.52 亿美元，这标志着欧洲和美洲长达六年多的法律调查结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/glencore-ordered-to-pay-150-million-by-swiss-in-criminal-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
