    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市普遍下跌，跌至 2 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/european-stocks-drop-most-in-two-years-as-global-rout-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济放缓的担忧引发全球经济进一步衰退，欧洲股市下跌，导致地区基准指数跌至 2 月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/european-stocks-drop-most-in-two-years-as-global-rout-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:58:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股市陷入风险抛售：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对世界最大经济体增长放缓的担忧引发了人们对今年股市上涨过快的猜测，市场风险较高领域的抛售进一步加剧，股市暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币暴跌，以太币遭遇 2021 年以来最大跌幅，加密货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bitcoin-btc-drops-below-59-000-after-worst-week-since-ftx-collapse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，加密货币受到全球市场避险情绪的冲击，比特币一度下跌超过 16%，排名第二的以太币则遭遇了 2021 年以来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bitcoin-btc-drops-below-59-000-after-worst-week-since-ftx-collapse</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 23:52:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股暴跌，标普 500 指数或创 2022 年以来最大单日跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/us-stock-futures-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济放缓和技术板块过热上涨的担忧加剧，投资者准备迎接连续数日的波动，美国股市周一遭受重创，成为全球股市抛售潮的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/us-stock-futures-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 22:05:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
